title: Meet Your Sweet
description: "Are You Feeling Confused & Hopeless In a Relationship That Has Lost Its Joy & Feels a Million Miles Away From What It Used To Be?" "Perhaps You Have Tried Everything You Can To Fix Things But Your Partner Just Doesn't Seem To Notice Or Care..." Here's something that will surely help you solve whatever your love issues in life: Meet Your Sweet! Meet Your Sweet is Slade and Mirabelle's latest creation and offers to re-think the way in which males approach dating, seduction, and associations with females. This book is an Ultimate Attraction Transformation Series that offer readers tips and tricks to transform their personality to attract the persons of opposite sex
